import './^3athon.css'; const _3athon = () => { return
^3athon
2022
The first inter-school 3x3 and 2x2 cubing competition of TheSune was organized in collaboration with the school tech club – Code Warriors. The event was held in two parts : The Online Prelims and The Offline Finals. This event was a huge success and saw participation of most major schools of Delhi.
^3athon 2 x 2
1. Garv Jhuremalani (Delhi Public School, R.K. Puram)
2. Rehan Mongia (Airforce Bal Bharti School)
3. Pranav Chandra (Delhi Public School, Mathura Road)
^3athon 3 x 3
1. Shreyas Anand (Air Force Bal Bharati School)
2. Nikhil Lal (Delhi Public School, R.K. Puram)
3. Arush Kashyap (Amity International School Gurugram Sector 46)
2023
The second inter-school 3x3 and 2x2 cubing competition of The Sune was organized in collaboration with the school's technology club – Code Warriors. The event was held in two phases, The Online Prelims and The Offline Finals. The event consisted of 3 categories namely, 2x2, 3x3 and x³. The event was a massive success and saw participation of various prominent schools of Delhi. The results of the event were as follows:
^3athon 2 x 2
1. Garv Jhuremalani (Delhi Public School, R.K. Puram)
2. Pranav Chandra (Delhi Public School, Dwarka)
3. Arnav Bansal (Delhi Public School, Noida)
^3athon 3 x 3
1. Ronit Arora (Rukmini Devi Public School)
2. Nikhil Lal (Delhi Public School, R.K. Puram)
3. Rehan Mongia (Air Force Bal Bharti School)
^3athon x³ (team event)
1. Nikhil Lal and Garv Jhuremalani (Delhi Public School, R.K. Puram)
2. Prisha Bhatia and Arush Kashyap (Amity International Sector 46)
3. Rehan Mongia and Nakshastra Aggarwal (Air Force Bal Bharti School)
; } export default _3athon;
